        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "And quoth another,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "'My blamers say of me, 'He is consoled,' And lie!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "And again,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "And again,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "Such are the excellencies of the youth which women do not own, and they more than suffice to give those the preference over these.' She replied, 'Allah give thee health!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "The girl is soft of speech, fair of form, like a branchlet of basil, with teeth like chamomile petals and hair like halters wherefrom to hang hearts.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000017_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000017_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "Her body is well formed and with sloping shoulders dight; she hath a nose like the edge of a sword shining bright and a forehead brilliant white and eyebrows which unite and eyes stained by Nature's hand black as night.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000017_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000017_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "In her all beauties to conclusion come, and she is the centre of attraction to traveller and stay at home.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "When it was the Four Hundred and Twenty second Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "So, O miserable! where are mortal men beside the Jinn?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "Knowest thou not that puissant princes and potent Kings before women ever humbly bend and on them for delight depend?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000019_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000019_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "Indeed, they seduce the sage and send the saint to shame and bring the wealthy to want and plunge the fortune favoured into penury.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000019_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000019_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "Yet for all this, the wise but redouble in affection of them and honour; nor do they count this oppression or dishonour.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000019_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000019_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "How many a man for them hath offended his Maker and called down on him self the wrath of his father and mother!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000019_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000019_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "And all this because of the conquest of their love over hearts.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "As for what thou sayest of a youth's first hair on cheek and lips and how they add to his beauty and loveliness, by Allah, thou strayest from the straight path of sooth and sayest that which is other than the truth; for whiskers change the charms of the comely into ugliness (quoting these couplets),",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "When it was the Four Hundred and Twenty third Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000025_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000025_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "How well saith the poet,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "Then said she, 'O folk ye have made me to break the bounds of modesty and the circle of free born women and indulge in idle talk of chambering and wantonness, which beseemeth not people of learning.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "But the breasts of free borns are the sepulchres of secrets' and such conversations are in confidence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "Quoth Abu Suwayd, \"I and a company of my friends, entered a garden one day to buy somewhat of fruit; and we saw in a corner an old woman, who was bright of face, but her head hair was white, and she was combing it with an ivory comb.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "When it was the Four Hundred and Twenty fourth Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "I cried, 'By Allah, favoured art thou for an old woman!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "How sincere art thou in thine after pine for forbidden pleasures and how false is thy pretence of repentance from frowardness!'\" And another tale is that of",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60781_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60781/6346_60781_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "Answered she, \"Allah exalt the Emir!\" and recited this verse in reply,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60784_000000_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60784/6346_60784_000000_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "When it was the Four Hundred and Thirty third Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60784_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60784/6346_60784_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "She said, It hath reached me, O auspicious King, that the King and the Wazir and his son ceased not to dwell in all solace and in the greatest happiness awhile, till the King fell ill and his sickness grew on him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60784_000001_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60784/6346_60784_000001_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "Then said the King to the Emirs, \"Do ye all accept of him?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60784_000001_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60784/6346_60784_000001_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "Then the King did likewise and bade him take his seat on the throne of kingship; whereupon they all arose and kissed King Hasan's hands and did homage to him, and swore lealty to him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60784_000001_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60784/6346_60784_000001_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "And the new King dispensed justice among the people that day in fashion right royal, and invested the grandees of the realm in splendid robes of honour.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60784_000001_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60784/6346_60784_000001_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "When the Divan broke up, he went in to and kissed the hands of his father in law who spake thus to him, \"O my son, look thou rule the lieges in the fear of Allah;\"--And Shahrazad perceived the dawn of day and ceased to say her permitted say.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60784_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60784/6346_60784_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "When it was the Four Hundred and Thirty fourth Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60784_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60784/6346_60784_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "He passed the day in dispensing justice among the folk, bidding to graciousness and forbidding ungraciousness and appointing to place and displacing, till day end, when the Divan broke up, after the goodliest fashion, and all the troops withdrew and each went his own way.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60784_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60784/6346_60784_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "So they laid him out and shrouded and buried him and held over him readings and perlections of the Koran, to the end of the customary forty days.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60784_000003_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60784/6346_60784_000003_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "And King Hasan, son of the Wazir, reigned in his stead, and his subjects joyed in him and all his days were gladness; moreover, his father ceased not to be his chief Wazir on his right hand, and he took to himself another Wazir, to be at his left hand.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
