        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "His years waxed great; his bones became wasted and his back bent; weakness and weariness grew upon him, and he feared the loss of his wealth and possessions, seeing he had no child whom he might make his heir and by whom his name should be remembered.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6346_60784_000013_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6346/60784/6346_60784_000013_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6346",
        "content": "In due time she finished her months and, casting her burden, bore a male child as he were a slice of the moon; whereupon the merchant fulfilled his vows in his gratitude to Allah, (to whom be honour and glory!) and gave alms and clothed the widow and the orphan.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
